  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catale is a deck building game that combines CCG and RogueLike. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/a8c6f27ecc801da9714c4fa2d34feae8.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/a8c6f27ecc801da9714c4fa2d34feae8.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=530 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/b4ff5ac2f120e7dd81793da46fe43409.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/b4ff5ac2f120e7dd81793da46fe43409.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=526 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breathtaking battle</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/324812468481f129ca4d049bebe2d44b.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/324812468481f129ca4d049bebe2d44b.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically place units in a field of 10 compartments, check enemy units, and attack to destroy enemy heroes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Units attack units facing each other, so you have to think carefully and use your card! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Please, legendary card...!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/25563ed6d4b8353f5f4e2391ff4acc9d.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/25563ed6d4b8353f5f4e2391ff4acc9d.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=198 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won the battle, so you have to take the spoils.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the pack and strengthen the deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope you get a legendary card...!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...there is no golden legendary card, unfortunately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Deck building that's fun to think about</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/e605a68539a6e20ec5b575f44afe5f76.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/e605a68539a6e20ec5b575f44afe5f76.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The way the deck is constructed in Catale borrows from the traditional CCG method. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you open the pack and get a card, you choose 20 of them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because the cards you get are different, the 'best deck' cannot exist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun collecting cards, and thinking about what cards to put in your deck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own card.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/f353c77f34b06b3f804c122f9f550db6.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/f353c77f34b06b3f804c122f9f550db6.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=428 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/7b0390d290d6e8c72eb670f93c1e74a7.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/7b0390d290d6e8c72eb670f93c1e74a7.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own card. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize cost, power, health, keywords, and all effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catale is a deck building game that combines CCG and RogueLike. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/a8c6f27ecc801da9714c4fa2d34feae8.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/a8c6f27ecc801da9714c4fa2d34feae8.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=530 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/b4ff5ac2f120e7dd81793da46fe43409.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/b4ff5ac2f120e7dd81793da46fe43409.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=526 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breathtaking battle</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/324812468481f129ca4d049bebe2d44b.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/324812468481f129ca4d049bebe2d44b.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically place units in a field of 10 compartments, check enemy units, and attack to destroy enemy heroes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Units attack units facing each other, so you have to think carefully and use your card! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Please, legendary card...!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/25563ed6d4b8353f5f4e2391ff4acc9d.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/25563ed6d4b8353f5f4e2391ff4acc9d.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=198 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won the battle, so you have to take the spoils.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the pack and strengthen the deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope you get a legendary card...!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...there is no golden legendary card, unfortunately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Deck building that's fun to think about</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/e605a68539a6e20ec5b575f44afe5f76.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/e605a68539a6e20ec5b575f44afe5f76.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The way the deck is constructed in Catale borrows from the traditional CCG method. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you open the pack and get a card, you choose 20 of them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because the cards you get are different, the 'best deck' cannot exist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun collecting cards, and thinking about what cards to put in your deck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own card.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/f353c77f34b06b3f804c122f9f550db6.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/f353c77f34b06b3f804c122f9f550db6.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=428 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras/7b0390d290d6e8c72eb670f93c1e74a7.avif?t=1755404881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922690/extras_big/7b0390d290d6e8c72eb670f93c1e74a7.avif?t=1755404881 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own card. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize cost, power, health, keywords, and all effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
